{"tid":1358170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（12:00）【最緊要人無事】@屯門良田","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:26:47.000Z","uid":107060,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"717ef0071f37ef35432ce6ba8fa593526f7c6d3e","tid":1358170,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:13:37.000Z","msg":"Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n<br />\n（12:00）【最緊要人無事】@屯門良田<br />\n<br />\n剛才屯門良田村，有一位黑衫街坊被幾個白衫人攻擊，期間差點被拖進村內，幸好及時有人出手幫助。該名街坊手腳擦傷，暫時安全，希望傷勢沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n但白衫人在捉人期間，曾經搶手機拍攝一些「溝通群組」，甚至想搶走電話，最終手機被毀爛後奪回。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有一些街坊均報稱收到「133」的匿名電話，亦有出言問候及套料等。<br />\n<br />\n大家千萬要注意個人安全，一定要避免落單工作，而曾進入一些地區群組，亦要注意小心個人資訊外洩，謹慎行事，平安順利。"},{"pid":"07d03942456f89dae6d86b32e54d87fc2e33954e","tid":1358170,"uid":107060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:14:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家千萬要注意個人安全，一定要避免落單工作，而曾進入一些地區群組，亦要注意小心個人資訊外洩，謹慎行事，平安順利。</span></span>"},{"pid":"6078a75fc4d20b457c2a3f124ea640c6f9e1c0f8","tid":1358170,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12730e213a68df4eabbcea648a4a579f7ad66002","tid":1358170,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c455408b3b39aa97eec2f991510fad6f084a934f","tid":1358170,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648c00db5852eed3cc16b928e52782f5b1c08e6d","tid":1358170,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69181fa2069c081b73c314ce470bdaebf75bd35b","tid":1358170,"u